reviewText: The case might have Espanol on it , butt Sara Jean is all American. 5 Golden Stars !!!  Thank you Ms. Underwood.

Sara Jean Underwood, currently appearing on "The Attack of the Show", is an absolute beauty to behold.  Her appearances on the G4 show are always both entertaining and humorous, which led me to google her name.  I was extremely grateful to find this dvd on Amazon.  Watch the G4 show a couple of times and then decide if seeing her is worth the expenditure!  It's worth it!
